snippet.title: TRIALS of FIRE - Alchemist Reveal | E3 2019 (PC)
snippet.description:
TRIALS of FIRE - Alchemist Reveal | E3 2019

The Alchemist is all about embracing and mastering randomness! Able to create cards from nothing to suit the situation as well as dealing out random and potentially massive amounts of damage.
